    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('Prepare Variables').item.json.email }}",
        "subject": "About your Competitor FAQ Report",
        "message": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><title>About your Competitor FAQ Report</title></head><body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333;\"><table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><p>Hi there,</p><p>We ran the report on the URLs you submitted, but we couldn't find any FAQ content on those pages.</p><p>This usually happens when:</p><ul><li>The URL points to a homepage rather than a specific FAQ or Help page</li><li>The FAQ content is loaded dynamically (JavaScript-rendered)</li><li>The page doesn't have a dedicated FAQ section</li></ul><p>Try resubmitting with the direct URL of the FAQ or Help page, for example:<br><em>example.com/faq</em> or <em>example.com/help</em></p><p>If you need a hand finding the right URLs, just reply and we'll help you out.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 20px; background-color: #FF7433; text-align: center;\"><p style=\"color: white; margin: 0;\">Best regards,</p><p style=\"color: white; margin: 4px 0 0;\"><strong>The Intelligent Resources Team</strong></p></td></tr></table></body></html>",
